          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This method decrements the sudden termination counter. When the termination counter reaches ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " the application allows sudden termination.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "By default the sudden termination counter is set to 1. This can be overridden in your application Info.plist. See ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsprocessinfo#1651129",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " for more information and debugging suggestions.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
